headline: South Fork Wind Onshore Infrastructure Buildout Propels Eversource to Project of the Year Award
summary: HARTFORD, Conn. & BOSTON, November 14, 2024--Eversource (NYSE: ES) has been awarded the "New York Project of the Year" from the Engineering News-Record (ENR) for its leading efforts building the onshore infrastructure for the South Fork Wind project, the first commercial scale offshore wind project in the United States.
